 Children offer sweets and fruits to their mother on the occasion of Mother's Day in Kathmandu, Nepal, April 30, 2022. (Photo by Hari Maharjan/Xinhua)  People bathe beside the pond at the Matatirtha temple in Kathmandu, Nepal, April 30, 2022. Nepalese Hindu devotees bathe in the pond, make offerings and pay homage to their departed mothers as they mark the Mother's Day in Nepal. (Photo by Hari Maharjan/Xinhua)